'Stuart Daniel Baker', better known by his stage name, 'Unknown Hinson', is a
comedic country musician, songwriter, and voice actor. He is perhaps best known
for his role as the voice of Early Cuyler on the Adult Swim cartoon series
[[Squidbillies]].
